1 D. For purposes of this section, “proof of citizenship” shall
2 mean the requirements for proof of citizenship pursuant to the
3 provisions of the REAL ID Act of 2005, Public Law No. 109-13.
4 E. The Secretary shall promulgate rules and procedures as
5 necessary to effectuate the provisions of this section.
